elements.title: Hum­ber­tium covidum
elements.contents: ... that the flatworm Hum­ber­tium covidum (pictured), named after the COVID-19 pandemic, was classified in a study written mostly during the initial lockdown?

elements.title: B. J. Habibie Bridge
